1. ProcessVideoActivity - records video, has only 1 button for starting/finishing video recording
- Show preview
- Start recording
- Stop recording
- Save images for collage (don't save video)

2. CollageCompositionActivity - allows to select pattern of collage, and set filters
- Get images and show preview of collage with default pattern
- Pattern can be changed by selecting from list, and preview changes appropriately
- Each image in collage can be selected by checkbox for applying a filter
- After applying a filter preview is changed
- When all possible adjusting are performed user presses button "finish" and navigates to the final image

3. CollagePreviewActivity - shows result of work on previous steps
- Preview of the final image
- The final image can be shared